paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the fluorescence properties of monomeric transthyretin (M-TTR) and its variants, focusing on conformational changes. No specific genetic variants in the TTR gene are reported.

challenges: The paper did not report any specific genetic variants in the TTR gene.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper focused on the biochemical properties of TTR and its variants but did not provide genetic variant data.
